org.ensor.robots.primitives

Class Atom

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ensor.robots.primitives.Atom
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoolAtom, DictionaryAtom, IntAtom, ListAtom, RealAtom, StringAtom

    public abstract class Atom
extends Object
    An atom is the primitive abstract data container for events. It consists of a type and derived classes hold the actual data associated with the atom.
    Author:
    Jon
